68
00:04:12,650 --> 00:04:14,550
Tadeto to tiež nepôjde.

69
00:04:14,550 --> 00:04:16,310
M-musíme sa odtiaľto dostať!

70
00:04:20,920 --> 00:04:21,950
Tati!

71
00:04:22,590 --> 00:04:23,490
Sayuri!

72
00:04:23,490 --> 00:04:26,490
